      "text": "We have heard of heroes in ages past,\nof twelve true thanes under the turning stars,\nthe Lord’s own champions. Their glory lived on\nin the grim struggle where standards clashed.\nTheir lots were laid out as the Lord Himself,\nHeaven’s High King, handed them their fates.\nFamed were those men across the fields of earth,\nbold-hearted leaders, keen in the battle-press,\nwhere hand guarded helmet on the field of doom,\nand the broad shield was broken in the bitter fray."
